Ing '''Bhopāl''' {{audio|Bhopal.ogg|pronunciation}} ([[Hindi]]: भोपाल {{IPA2|bʰoːpɑːl}}) metung yang lakanbalen o ciudad king kalibudtang [[India]]. Tungku (capitoliu) ne ning [[w:Indian state|estadu]] ning [[Madhya Pradesh]] at pun tanggapan pang-kapanibalan ning [[Bhopal District]] ampong [[Bhopal Division]]. Ing Bhopal ing kaduang pekamaragul a lakanbalen king Madhya Pradesh kaibat ning [[Indore]]. Pikabaluan ya ing Bhopal antimong ''City of Lakes'' (Lakanbalen da reng Dano) uling mitmu yang natural a dano ampo retang gewa ning tau.<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.southasiabiz.com/2006/10/city_of_lakes_mosques_and_temp.html
|title=City of Lakes
|accessdate=2007-04-12
}}</ref> 

Mibili keti ing pansin ning kabilugan a yatu uling ketang [[w:Bhopal disaster|kalamidad ning Bhopaol]], a miliari aniang siningo ing mapanganib a  [[methyl isocyanate]] gas ibat king planta ning [[Union Carbide]] (a ngeni bandi na na ning [[Dow Chemical Company]]) aniang bengi ning [[Diciembre 3]], [[1984]].

